{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/hidden-a-element-what-a-best-choice/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"the-problem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-problem\" aria-label=\"the problem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Problem</h2>\n<p>We usually are use the following ways to hidden a element:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">// 1\n<span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n// 2\n<span class=\"token property\">visibility</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden\n\n// 3\n<span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0</code></pre></div>\n<p>The ways above is work fine but what is the best choice?</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-deep-part\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-deep-part\" aria-label=\"the deep part permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Deep Part</h2>\n<p>With display: none. We remove the element from DOM. It is bad pattern, because this way make the DOM re-calculate the part of DOM was changed, in a short word: reflow. Beside it will make the layout is lagging because the DOM lost a element.</p>\n<p>The rescue come with opacity and visibility. It is just hidden element, not remove from DOM, just repaint. This way will improve the performance and not make the layout change</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-conclusion\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-conclusion\" aria-label=\"the conclusion permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Conclusion</h2>\n<p>I recommend use the opacity or visibility</p>","excerpt":"The Problem We usually are use the following ways to hidden a element: The ways above is work fine but what is the best choice? The Deep…","fields":{"slug":"/hidden-a-element-what-a-best-choice/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The ways to hidden a element and what a best choice","date":"April 11, 2021","tags":["javascript","html","css"],"description":"The easy thing but must think to use it","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/36dadcfa302972fac06dbafa8da058e0/92ab1/html-icon.png","srcSet":"/static/36dadcfa302972fac06dbafa8da058e0/92ab1/html-icon.png 1x,\n/static/36dadcfa302972fac06dbafa8da058e0/668a7/html-icon.png 1.5x"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/hidden-a-element-what-a-best-choice/","